1 written approval of the Secretary of the Department of Adult Correction. Custodial officials
2 employed by an out-of-state correctional facility are agents of the Secretary of the Department
3 of Adult Correction and may use those procedures for use of force authorized by the Secretary
4 of the Department of Adult Correction not inconsistent with the laws of the State of situs of the
5 facility to defend themselves, to enforce the observance of discipline in compliance with
